childMarkdownRemark.html: Muthu is a fantastic resource for Technology . He is very good in implementing new Technology solutions for an organization to drive efficiency and improve bottom line. In Ad2pro , Muthu implemented an amazing HRMS (Human resource management system) and also made enhancements to existing Work Flow for improving productivity . Muthu was always interacting with Senior Leadership team to take inputs and was recognized for his hard work and commitment . He played a vital role in all automation requirements in Ad2pro Muthu will be an asset for any organization and I wish him the very best.
